Package: mlstm
Type: Package
Title: Multilevel Supervised Topic Models with Multiple Outcomes in R
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Tomoya", "Himeno", email = "bd24f002@g.hit-u.ac.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for fitting latent Dirichlet allocation (LDA),
    supervised topic models (STM), and multilevel supervised topic models
    for text data with multiple outcome variables. Core estimation routines
    are implemented in C++ with Rcpp and support scalable variational
    inference and parallel computation.
